    "\"*\" represents variants of the word, such as plurals.",
    "To address the proposed research questions, a coding framework was developed through an iterative process to extract information from the included studies.",
    "Initially, one reviewer proposed a preliminary coding framework and piloted it by extracting information from 20 of the included studies.",
    "Refinements to the coding framework, such as adding new coding subsections, removing redundant or irrelevant ones, and defining coding categories within each subsection, were conducted.",
    "Subsequently, with the refined framework, two reviewers independently coded all the studies after training."
